item.description:
Hi all,

Since our season is coming to an end very quickly, I figured I would add in a few extra games! I am scheduling a game for Sunday afternoon in hopes enough people will sign up for us to play. 8 people need to sign up as DEFINITES in order for the game to happen. I would love to have 10 people though! We can all go out for some drink/apps after the game if anyone is interested in doing so. Please only respond YES if you are a DEFINITE YES!!

Thanks!!

Lori
